meta.about:
YDesign is a Los Angeles based handmade jewelry brand that uses premium wood & gold-plated hoop for earrings. 

20% of our profit will go to charity.  
For "Stand with Hong Kong" orders, we will donate 70% of our profit to 612 Humanitarian Fund.
